	<td bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	<td class="subjectbar" height="20" style="font-size: 8pt;padding-left:10px;" width="100%">
		Ideas to fix tanking issues

	</td>
	
		<td class="subjectbar" align=right style="padding:0px;padding-right:10px;">












		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 id="io_bwarriorbalancem1410_table" 
		
			onClick="setId('1410');showLiMenu(this,'io_bwarriorbalancem1410','right',false);" 
			onDblClick="setId('1410');showLiMenu(this,'io_bwarriorbalancem1410','right',false);" 
			
		>
		<tr class=clickable>
			
				<td nowrap><a class=subjectbar_text style='font-size: 8pt;'>Options</a></td>
				
			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
			<td><img src='/i/skins/default/button_options.gif' border=0 alt='Options' title='Options' width=11 height=28></td>
			<td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		</td></tr>
		
	<tr>
	
		<td class="msg_user_cell" width="150" valign=top>
		
			 









<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=42604'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#CCCC33;'>Katur</span></a>
			<br>
			
			<span style="font-size: 8pt;">
			Elder<br>
			
				Posts: 205<br>
				
				Registered: 06-12-2004
				
			</span>
			


			
			<br>
			
				<img src="/i/p.gif" height=8 width=150 border=0 alt=""><br>
				
			<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=42604'>







<img src="/eq/i/icons/Classes/warrior.gif" border=0 alt=""/></a><br>
			


			
			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=warriorbalance&message.id=1410#M1410">1</a> of 71
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 930 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		
				background-color: #050A0E; 
				
				 background-image: none;
				 
				background-repeat: repeat-x;
				" 
			>
			<DIV>First let me start by saying I think all 3 tank classes (warriors, shadowknights, and paladins) should be able to tank any group content. That is with the proper gear and group make up. I would like to see solid suggestions on how to fix this. It seems there are alot of whine threads out there and these possible solutions are spread out on them. I would like these suggestions to take into account the FIXING of defensive in these trials. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>My suggestions:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>1: Make plate armor actually mean something. Give all plate wearers the 5 percent mitigation that warriors currently have . Even clerics, and give the warrior 5 percent extra mitigation if you feel its warranted.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>2: Make shields worthy. Let them effect the die , or add in a block skill using a shield. All 3 tank classes should have this skill. Or any plate class bearing a shield should have this bonus. AC alone is a rediculous reason for anyone to equip a shield.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>3: Give knights a weaponshield(parry) type , or furious(riposte) type disc. Set its length and reuse timer according to wich they get.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>4: Come up with some benefits for both class to make them more viable in groups. I really like the idea of just having them grouped with you raising attack ac and hp. As&nbsp; has recently been noted. Knights was well known to inspire there fellow combatants.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>5: Give SKs more of a role. They seem very much in need of some attention compared to there counterpart IMO.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>6: BALANCE content before you sell it to us. This is the most rediculous thing that I would have to even ask , or say this. Its obvious these encounters need some attention , and are still unbalanced.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Lastly, please for all our sakes do not start flaming on this thread. Lets make this thread a friendly exchange of ideas. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Katur Carus
Proud leader of
Final Evolution
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
		<td class="msg_date_cell" valign=bottom nowrap>
		<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
		 <span class=date_text>06-23-2004</span> <span class=time_text>07:50 AM</span>
		</span>
		</td>

		
