<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>i think if you take away one of my advantages in a single group trial setting , then i think that the knights should lose an advantage for instance no matter what spell they cast they loose aggro including group heals simply because we lost our edge so i figure they should lose there's.</DIV>
