<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>As I mentioned in the Warrior board version of the thread which you referenced, Shadow Knights already have separate methods of&nbsp;producing pure hate on demand which would not be prevented by a spell like this.&nbsp;&nbsp;It seems much&nbsp;more flexible&nbsp;to use those separately when the need arises,&nbsp;including with&nbsp;an offense/defense combo&nbsp;spell like this one.</DIV>
