Why would you think that I think this is wrong when that's the exact point I was trying to make -- there's a raid where they are necessary, and there could be more instances like this implemented. I don't get why rp is such a weird idea ... you have a holy knight be more productive on unholy things --and vice versa -- pure tanking though should be a warriors domain. What do I mean by saying you sound like you've given up on a definitive role in the game? You want to give hybrids equal footing for pure tanking .. sorry, but our ac/hp difference + 5% mit is minimal -- there's no noticable difference in tanking between us without /def.<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
