<DIV>Raithe Council?&nbsp; War off tanked using fine steel weapons</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>CT in time?&nbsp; 1 knight tank/4+ war tanked wins</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So where is this "Nessacary"&nbsp; bit?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Dai</DIV><BR>
