<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Seeing that kngihts can now tank every other mob in each of those encounters now at the same level of progression that warriors are tanking those more knight friendly mobs, it can hardly be complained about that knights dont' have a perpetual lock on those mobs.&nbsp;&nbsp; Do you seriously think it's ok for knights to be able to replace warriors on every other mob in time, then complain that warriors can tank CT if they have to?</P>
